---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Arterial Hypertension — Dr Delhasse, Cardiologist" description="Hypertension, often silent, damages your organs. Specialist consultation with Dr Delhasse in Valais." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Arterial <span class="text-primary">Hypertension</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">The silent killer</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/svg/expertise/Hypertension-arterielle.svg" alt="Hypertension" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>A blood pressure of 100/70 mmHg is generally sufficient under normal conditions to adequately supply the body's organs, but it is not uncommon for higher values to be necessary, particularly in the elderly. If blood pressure rises above 140/90 mmHg, it damages organs such as the heart, arteries, kidneys, eyes and brain, and can even lead to complications in some cases.</p>

      <p>It is therefore important to consult a cardiologist if you have hypertension. During the consultation, you will benefit from an evaluation to identify possible causes, a personalised adjustment of your treatment, and specific advice on lifestyle changes needed to reduce your blood pressure.</p>

      <p>All these measures aim to control blood pressure effectively, prevent complications, protect your long-term health, and give your heart the peace it deserves.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/areas-of-expertise" class="btn btn--outline">&larr; All areas</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
